{"tid":1685912,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(罷搭黨鐵)感覺巴士呢期確係密咗車，整體時間快返唔少","createTime":"2019-10-31T23:52:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T05:53:26.000Z","uid":45255,"like":48,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"097984775100bf51baffaca464a81f0b07962b69","tid":1685912,"uid":45255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T23:52:11.000Z","msg":"利申: 機場返工撚，大欖隧道轉車<br />\n<br />\n九月同以前仲係喺轉車站排到打蛇餅，收工等成個鐘都未上到978/279X返上水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n10月開始快到基本上等15分內就上到，仲有一半時間有位坐<br />\n班次向來唔多密嘅978居然會打孖埋站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啜一聲就上到，快過轉黨鐵<br />\n<br />\n雖然擺黨鐵唔會窮到佢執笠<br />\n難得巴士公司都肯響影返加車而且偏來都偏黃，冇理由唔繼續多啲幫褲掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黨鐵站留返比Popo慢慢玩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBTW今早啱啱買完月票。明天112見<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1170d1bb56acef8b5c4f497835536b48d4b3613f","tid":1685912,"uid":45255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T23:54:11.000Z","msg":"記得隨咗克景之外，仲要睇著黨鐵折墮呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bfba8360fa3e7086390f6e36189d42c4a83f932","tid":1685912,"uid":41803,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T00:02:37.000Z","msg":"做生意，有人罷買你對手，當然就會順勢賣多幾件貨"},{"pid":"37664e35232619e458a1cfb4a28847986df070b6","tid":1685912,"uid":174432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T00:03:43.000Z","msg":"月票真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b4586918d8d5755ada59bef7baa353f19ffd599","tid":1685912,"uid":45255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9bfba8360fa3e7086390f6e36189d42c4a83f932","tid":1685912,"uid":41803,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime